                    "company": "Uitgeverij Van Oorschot",
                    "description": "In September 2019, my first book 'Opera - een geschiedenis in 27 sleutelwerken' (Opera - a history in 27 key works) was published by Uitgeverij Van Oorschot. It is a personal survey of 27 important works, giving my insights into the music and themes of the individual operas and in doing so charting the history and development of the genre. At this moment, I am working on my second book: 'Sluier van de tijd - het verborgen leven van kunst' (Veil of time - the hidden life of art).",
